title: calendar import
body:
trying to import my ics file i have this showing up in apache's error.log:

[thu jul 11 22:46:49 2013] [error] [client ip.ad.dr.ess] php fatal error:  call to a member function __get() on a non-object in /var/www/apps/calendar/lib/import.php on line 361, referer: http://obfuscated.url.com/index.php/apps/files
[thu jul 11 22:46:56 2013] [error] [client ip.ad.dr.ess] php fatal error:  call to a member function __get() on a non-object in /var/www/apps/calendar/lib/import.php on line 361, referer: http://obfuscated.url.com/index.php/apps/files
[thu jul 11 22:47:45 2013] [error] [client ip.ad.dr.ess] php fatal error:  call to a member function __get() on a non-object in /var/www/apps/calendar/lib/import.php on line 339, referer: http://obfuscated.url.com/index.php/apps/files
[thu jul 11 22:48:17 2013] [error] [client ip.ad.dr.ess] php fatal error:  call to a member function getcomponents() on a non-object in /var/www/apps/calendar/lib/import.php on line 114, referer: http://obfuscated.url.com/index.php/apps/files

for the public function guesscalendarcolor() and guesscalendarname() i set the functions to do nothing and return null;

then i get this:

php fatal error:  call to a member function getcomponents() on a non-object in /var/www/apps/calendar/lib/import.php on line 114, referer: http://obfuscated.url.com/index.php/apps/files


it won't read my ics file. file doesn't seem to be damaged.



system is 64-bit debian 7, apache2, sqlite.
